item.title: CVE-2019-0328|2024-08-04T17:44:16.476Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20process%20integration%20abap%20tests%20%28sap%20basis%29
item.description: ABAP Tests Modules (SAP Basis, versions 7.0, 7.1, 7.3, 7.31, 7.4, 7.5) of SAP NetWeaver Process Integration enables an attacker the execution of OS commands with privileged rights. An attacker could thereby impact the integrity and availability of the system.
